set-immediate-shim

Simple setImmediate shim

Install

$ npm install --save set-immediate-shim

Usage

var setImmediateShim = require('set-immediate-shim');

setImmediateShim(function () {
    console.log('2');
});

console.log('1');

//=> 1
//=> 2
